data.text:
New Jersey has been the birthplace of countless celebrities. It also has been the place where the rich and famous have settled down to raise a family or avoid the limelight.

We all know Bruce Springsteen, Jon Bon Jovi and Frank Sinatra were Jersey boys.

But we bet you didn't know that many of the boldface names in our list below had ties to the Garden State.

Take a look!
